Description: Both Wynn and Encore offer beautiful, temperature-controlled pools and Jacuzzi spas surrounded by immaculate gardens. Reserve a private cabana at the Wynn, Encore or Tower Suites pools complete with mini-Frige, plasma TV, plush chairs and sofas. The secluded, adults-only pools are an ideal retreat, and the Wynn European pool allows for topless sunbathing.
Location: 3131 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
